{{Quote|All I needed was to get past the outer group and into closer range. ''[&hellip;]'' All vessels: attack pattern ''d'moporai''.|Force Commander Mitth'raw'nuruodo|<ref name="OBF">[[Outbound Flight (novel)|''Outbound Flight'']]</ref>}}
'''Attack pattern ''d'moporai''''' was a [[Chiss Expansionary Defense Force]] battle tactic that involved [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] approaching from different vectors and launching [[Conner net|shock nets]] into a concentrated point of enemy fighter strength. This was done to create a hole in the enemy's fighter screen so that [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]] could advance.

